Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur5}{\3c&H880000&}小南被高中棒球感动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变回平时那安详的表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她战斗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人地战斗着…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕纪终于到达了没有病痛的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四坏球！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人出局 满垒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外球！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕纪去了 本应该很悲伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心中涌起的这份感情无法抑制下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外球！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小南
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 浅野同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一棒 左野手 田村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把球击飞！田村！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二棒 中坚手 柳泽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑出去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上垒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 田村！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按这个势头一口气反超吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 浅野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真神奇 疲劳一扫而光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉夕纪就守在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球！出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星出同学 状态不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是星出估计会被保送
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保送？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星出今天击出了2安打 状态绝佳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然一垒空着 对方大概会保险起见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以 这可是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然保送吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让对方后悔保送我们的四棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四坏球！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕纪去了 昨晚又一夜没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然完全感觉不到疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有这样的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 三个跑垒手都得分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六棒 游击手 樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐之助 别让这势头停！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的决赛 我认为应该换下祐之助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 即使输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为相信祐之助同学的成长让他出场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是经理人应该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐之助 把球击飞！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人出局 攻守互换！
